com.intel.icecp.core.channels

Class ChannelBase<T extends Message>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.icecp.core.channels.ChannelBase<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of message allowed on this channel
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Channel<T>, EventObservable, AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileChannel, LocalChannel, NdnNotificationChannel

    public abstract class ChannelBase<T extends Message>
extends Object
implements Channel<T>, EventObservable
    Base implementation of a channel; extend this in transport-specific sub-classes to simplify development.
